msgid ""
"When you are done making any changes to &MIME; types, you can click "
"<guibutton>Apply</guibutton> to make your changes permanent, but keep you in "
"this module."
msgstr ""
"Ketika kamu sudah selesai membuat perubahan apa pun terhadap tipe MIME, kamu "
